class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_5\">nos diste a beber un vino que aturde;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_6\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.6\" class=\"v19_60_6\">6<\/sup>la bandera que diste a tus fieles,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_6\">fue para que huyeran ante los arqueros. [<span class=\"it\">Pausa<\/span>]<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_7\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.7\" class=\"v19_60_7\">7<\/sup>S\u00e1lvanos con tu poder, ati\u00e9ndenos,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_7\">para que tus amados queden libres.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_8\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.8\" class=\"v19_60_8\">8<\/sup>Dios ha hablado en su santuario:<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_8\">\u201cMe regocijar\u00e9 al repartir Siqu\u00e9n,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_8\">cuando divida el valle de Sucot.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_9\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.9\" class=\"v19_60_9\">9<\/sup>M\u00edo es Galaad, m\u00edo es Manas\u00e9s,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_9\">es Efra\u00edn el yelmo de mi cabeza,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_9\">es Jud\u00e1 el cetro de mi poder;<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_10\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.10\" class=\"v19_60_10\">10<\/sup>es Moab la vasija en que me lavo,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_10\">sobre Edom arrojo mi sandalia,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_10\">sobre Filistea proclamo mi victoria\u201d.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_11\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.11\" class=\"v19_60_11\">11<\/sup>\u00bfQui\u00e9n me llevar\u00e1 a la ciudad fortificada,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_11\">qui\u00e9n me conducir\u00e1 hasta Edom?<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_12\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.12\" class=\"v19_60_12\">12<\/sup>S\u00f3lo t\u00fa, Dios, t\u00fa que nos rechazaste,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_12\">t\u00fa que ya no sales con nuestras tropas.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_13\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.13\" class=\"v19_60_13\">13<\/sup>Pr\u00e9stanos ayuda frente al enemigo,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_13\">pues de nada valen ayudas humanas.<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_14\"><sup id=\"Ps.60.14\" class=\"v19_60_14\">14<\/sup>Con Dios lograremos triunfar,<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"q\"><span class=\"v19_60_14\">\u00e9l humillar\u00e1 a nuestros enemigos.<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n","chapter":"60","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps.60","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.60.14","order":"19060","link":"spa-BHTI\/Ps\/60","display":"SALMOS 60","book":{"version_id":"173","name":"SALMOS","abbr":"Ps","ord":"19","book_group_id":"0","testament":"OT","id":"spa-BHTI:Ps","osis_end":"spa-BHTI:Ps.150.6"},"version":{"auditid":"0","display_abbreviation":"BHTI","version":"spa-BHTI","id":"spa-BHTI","name":"La Biblia Hispanoamericana (Traducci\u00f3n Interconfesional, versi\u00f3n hispanoamericana)","short_desc":null,"description":null,"active":1,"active_api":0,"listed":1,"orderindex":"99","lang":"spa","lang_code":"ISO 639-3","copyright":"<p>La Biblia Hispanoamericana (BHTI) Traducci&#243;n Interconfesional versi&#243;n hispanoamericana Copyright &#169; Sociedad B&#237;blica de Espa&#241;a, 2011 Utilizada con permiso<\/p>","contact_url":"http:\/\/sociedadbiblica.org","audio":"NONE","sections":[{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"OT","name":"Old Testament"},{"version_id":"spa-BHTI","id":"NT","name":"New Testament"}]},"audio":null,"prevChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.59","nextChapterId":"spa-BHTI:Ps.61","footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]},"footnotes":[],"crossreferences":[]}